**Lemma 1**.: _Fix some \(\mathbf{P}\in\boldsymbol{\mathcal{X}}\), and let \(\mathbf{X}_{t},\mathbf{X}_{t+1}\) be two successive iterates of (3MW), without any assumptions for the input sequence \(\hat{\mathbf{V}}_{t}\). We then have_

